            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Memoriae sanctissimae <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> Subri Secundini <lb n="3"/>flaminis et patroni provinciae <lb n="4"/>pietatis eloquentiae morum <lb n="5"/>magistri <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Subrius Severianus frater <lb n="7"/>inmatura eius morte deceptus </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> XXXX annis vixi<supplied reason="lost">t</supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="2"/>bis duo iungantur quos menses quattuor augent <lb n="3"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> mortique dies felix si longior aetas <lb n="4"/>mansisset quam dura sibi fortuna negavit <lb n="5"/>o miseros homines <note>sic</note> vivunt qui vivere nolunt <lb n="6"/>vivere qui debent fato moriuntur acerbo
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Bearbeiterin: V. Pettirossi.</p>
            </div>
